Package: boundHTS
Type: Package
Title: Building Hierarchical Coherent Densities for Bounded Variables
Author: Hannah Comiskey [aut, cre], David Frazier [aut], Ole Maneesoonthorn [aut]
Maintainer: Hannah Comiskey <hannahcomiskey68@gmail.com>
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Hannah",
                      family = "Comiskey",
                      role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
                      email = "hannahcomiskey68@gmail.com"),
             person(given = "David T.",
                      family = "Frazier",
                      role = "aut"),
             person(given = "Ole",
                      family = "Maneesoonthorn",
                      role = "aut"))
Description: Tools for post-hoc reconciliation of hierarchical forecast distributions for discrete or bounded data. The methods construct coherent and distributionally consistent forecasts while preserving the support of the underlying distributions. This enables hierarchical probabilistic forecasting for count and proportion time series where Gaussian assumptions are inappropriate.
